sequenceDiagram
  participant User as user
  participant AgentLoop as Agent Loop
  participant Model as Model
  participant Tools as Tool Runtime
  participant FS as Project environment

  User->>AgentLoop: Fix failed tests
  AgentLoop->>Model: Goals + History + Available Tools
  Model-->>AgentLoop: tool_intent: run_tests
  AgentLoop->>Tools: Verify parameters and permissions
  Tools->>FS: Execute test command
  FS-->>Tools: Failure log
  Tools-->>AgentLoop: observation
  AgentLoop->>Model: Backfill failure log
  Model-->>AgentLoop: tool_intent: read_file
